{"title":"Readers’ Rides: Thomas’ 1995 Kona Cinder Cone Restoration","link":"https://theradavist.com/1995-kona-cinder-cone-restoration/","date":1699626609000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>When it comes to vintage mountain bikes of the mid-1990s, it’s hard to not mention the 1995 Kona Cinder Cone. It had one of the most unique stances at the time and the painted to match fork and stem were straight from the playbook of something small time framebuilders were and are still doing today. Thomas sent in his Cinder Cone and the final product included some clever metalwork. Read on to find out and for some of Thomas’ delicious photos!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2667&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,2400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1780&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/a02deca3-b5f0-4d8c-ac96-0eadab16f5e0_53262389072_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,2048&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2667&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,2400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1780&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/82e30d9c-4da1-4d63-9f27-45c9d010b93d_53263618669_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,2048&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1546\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?w=1546&amp;quality=75 1546w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1696&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,3313&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1272&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,2981&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,2211&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=700,1159&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=927,1536&amp;quality=75 927w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7402ecb1-599c-4eca-9b63-b5687249b1d8_53262386377_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1236,2048&amp;quality=75 1236w\" /></p>\n<p>Founded by Jake Heilbron and Dan Gerhard in 1988,  Kona began its foray into production mountain bikes with steel hardtails and rigid bikes. Gerhard and Heilbron, along with Joe Murray, were the first brand to produce an entire catalog of sloping top tube MTBS. Later, Paul Brodie helped Kona further develop its lineup. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7614_53277483971_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>One such bike was the Cinder Cone and in 1995, it was all the rage. If you rode bikes back then, chances are you knew someone that owned one.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2667&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,2400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1780&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7fc84423-56b3-4c52-b8cd-243f481d921a_53263266701_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,2048&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/42aa5e62-06aa-415f-8488-6a63ac4eb99c_53262386747_o-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/42aa5e62-06aa-415f-8488-6a63ac4eb99c_53262386747_o-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/42aa5e62-06aa-415f-8488-6a63ac4eb99c_53262386747_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/42aa5e62-06aa-415f-8488-6a63ac4eb99c_53262386747_o-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2667&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/42aa5e62-06aa-415f-8488-6a63ac4eb99c_53262386747_o-scaled.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/42aa5e62-06aa-415f-8488-6a63ac4eb99c_53262386747_o-scaled.jpg