eradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7220c806-a868-4c53-9dbd-d3afb33ca500_53263560903_o-scaled.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7220c806-a868-4c53-9dbd-d3afb33ca500_53263560903_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/7220c806-a868-4c53-9dbd-d3afb33ca500_53263560903_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,2048&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>I LOVE that Kona matched the fork and stem, so I  chopped the stem and fillet brazed on a new Paragon Machine Works stem clamp, and repainted it to match the original. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7694_53277478961_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7689_53277840719_o-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7689_53277840719_o-scaled.jpg?w=1707&amp;quality=75 1707w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7689_53277840719_o-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/202