dia.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7728_53276603882_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7728_53276603882_o.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7728_53276603882_o.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7728_53276603882_o.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7728_53276603882_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7708_53277945050_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7670_53276598617_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1349\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?resize=1024,691&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?resize=768,518&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?resize=1800,1214&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?resize=1335,900&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?resize=700,472&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7634_53277768198_o.jpg?resize=1536,1036&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1267\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?resize=1024,649&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?resize=768,487&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?resize=1800,1140&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?resize=1335,846&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?resize=700,443&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/img_7641_53277489391_o.jpg?resize=1536,973&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Check out more images at <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/193440277@N04/albums/72177720311973286/with/53277953685/\" target=\"_blank\">my Flickr</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Build Spec:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>19″ double butted steel frameset with Kona Project Two fork</li>\n<li>Modified Kona Velocity stem with PMW 31.8 clamp (From 125 to 90mm)</li>\n<li>Bassi Bobby bars (with most of the graphics removed)</li>\n<li>ESI Racers Edge grips</li>\n<li>Shimano Ultegra 8 speed bar end shifters (friction front, indexed rear)</li>\n<li>Paul Thumbies (with brass barrel adjusters from Donhou)</li>\n<li>Paul Canti short pull levers</li>\n<li>Simworks brass ferrules</li>\n<li>Ritchey Logic cantilever brakes with Koolstop salmon pads</li>\n<li>Shimano XT (M737) hubs</li>\n<li>Straight gauge spokes and brass nipples (14g rear, 15g front)</li>\n<li>Mavic U.B. Control 26″ rims</li>\n<li>Rene Herse 2.3″ Humptulips Ridge tires</li>\n<li>Shimano LX (M566) Front Derailleur</li>\n<li>Shimano XT (M737) Rear Derailleur</li>\n<li>Sugino Impel square taper triple crankset</li>\n<li>Brass extractor caps</li>\n<li>Kona Race Light seatpost</li>\n<li>Brooks Cambium C15 Saddle</li>\n<li>Pealgo Stainless commuter rack</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p><em>We’d like to thank all of you who <a href=\"mailto:readersrides@theradavist.com\" target=\"_blank\">submitted Readers Rides</a> builds to be shared here at The Radavist. The response has been incredible and we have so many to share over the next few months. Feel free to submit your bike, listing details, components, and other information. You can also include a portrait of yourself with your bike and your Instagram account! Please, shoot landscape-orientation photos, not portrait. Thanks!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/1995-kona-cinder-cone-restoration/\">Readers’ Rides: Thomas’ 1995 Kona Cinder Cone Restoration</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"c81973d336d2059aa6603d6788370789bee35ac3f22407d5e67fa92280d59e4f","category":"Cycling"}